## Don't

- Don't edit shipped Alembic migrations.
- Don't construct new `Settings()` instances.
- Don't call `litellm.completion` / `OllamaClient` directly.
- Don't write to Iceberg via raw PyIceberg.
- Don't pickle ORM objects across tasks (pass IDs, re-fetch).
- Don't put strategy logic in API routes.
- Don't break the progress-bus payload shape
  (`{task_id, stage, message, timestamp, **extras}`).
- Don't add new diagram formats. Mermaid only.
